high_descs: Turn around and walk to the front of the stove.
Pick up the pan to the right of the stove.
Turn around and move to the front of the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge and remove it.
Turn to the left and approach the sink.
Place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill the pan in the fridge and put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside, then take it out.
Turn around, step forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter in front of the pan on your left.
Grab the pan from the counter.
Walk to the fridge on your left.
Place the pan in the fridge, then remove it.
Walk to the kitchen sink on your left.
Put the pan in the plate.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and put it in the sink.
